n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"la\">Latin\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"he\">Hebrew\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"phn\">Phoenician\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xpu\">Punic\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"osc\">Oscan\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xly\">Elymian\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"scx\">Sikel\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"sxc\">Sikan\u003C/language>\n            \u003C/langUsage>\n            \u003CtextClass>\n                \u003Ckeywords scheme=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins.html\">\n                    \u003Cterm ana=\"#function.funerary\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/92.html\">funerary\u003C/term>\n                \u003C/keywords>\n            \u003C/textClass>\n        \u003C/profileDesc>\n        \u003CrevisionDesc status=\"draft\">\n            \u003ClistChange>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2016-12-03\" who=\"#JCu\">James Cummings autogenerated EpiDoc output from database\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2017-06-11\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag revised the EpiDoc and added translation\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2017-07-06\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag added elements for parallel Italian\u003C/change>\n            \t   \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-05\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova normalised Unicode\u003C/change>\n            \t   \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-08\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova updated list of languages\u003C/change>\n            \t\u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-20\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova added EDCS numbers\u003C/change>\n\t\t\u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography\u003C/change>\n\t    \u003Cchange when=\"2020-12-18\" who=\"#system\">Updated Zenodo DOI\u003C/change>\n            \t\u003Cchange when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references\u003C/change>\n\t\u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic003223_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic003223.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cab>\u003Clb n=\"1\"/>Δαίμοσι\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>χθονίοις\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>\n                    \u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\n                        \u003Cname>Καιλία\u003C/name>\n                        ·\n                        \u003Cname>Ἑορτὴ\u003C/name>\n                    \u003C/persName>\n                    ·\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\"/>ἐβίωσε · ἔτη · ο’\n                    \u003Clb n=\"5\"/>\n                    \u003CpersName type=\"attested\">Βλάστη\u003C/persName>\n                    · θυγάτηρ\n                    \u003Clb n=\"6\"/>μητρὶ · εὐσεβεσ\n                    \u003Clb n=\"7\" break=\"no\"/>τάτῃ · ἔποισε\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--external apparatus criticus (if applicable)-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cp>To the underworld spirits. Kailia Heorte lived for 70 years. Blaste, her daughter, made this for a\n                    devoted mother.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"it\" resp=\"#SA\">\n                \u003Cp>Agli Spiriti sotterranei. Kailia Heorte ha vissuto per 70 anni. Blaste, sua figlia, ha fatto questo\n                    per la madre devota.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n                \u003Cp>The phrasing of this text, with the unusual Δαίμοσι χθονίοις (one other Sicilian instance, IG\n                    XIV.294, from Alcamo), instead of the more normal Θεοῖς Καταχθονίοις (both imitating the Latin Dis\n                    Manibus), the uncommon ἐβίωσε instead of ἔζησε (‘she lived’, Latin vixit), and the unusual form\n                    ἔποισε (‘she made’, usually ἐποίησε, Latin fecit) all suggest the influence of typical Latin\n                    formulaic construction (compare nos. 18-21). Both Heorte and Blaste are rare names, mostly found in\n                    the eastern Mediterranean in the imperial period, but each is attested once also in Siracusa. Given\n                    that Kailia is the Latin Caelia, it is possible that Heorte is intended as a translation of the\n                    Latin Festa.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IMusCatania\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>65\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/2EUC82DH\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Libertini\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1931\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>46 no.11 = Libertini (1981) 96\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/T67M4XMU\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001870\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001870\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
